Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.40,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕嚕咕嚕轉上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.51,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:59.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:03.25,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
